This add-on allows to replace or update an existing bookmark with minimal click count.

How to install:
Open a link:
https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/replace-bookmark/
and click "+ Add to Firefox"

Usage:
1. Press on add-on icon in toolbar.
2. Update a bookmark with three options:
    - Press Ctrl-Space (or Cmd-Space on MacOS)
    - Double-click on desired bookmark to update.
    - Click a button

